content.detailedDescription: I was 11 years old , playing pee-wee league base ball , south of eugene at a baseball diamond, we were playing ball, when all players stopped ,then i wondered what is happening , why did everyone stop playing ball, i looked , everyone in the bleachers was looking up, and all in the field were looking up, i looked up also, there was a large glowing ball of light hovering over the field, no sound at all, it hovered for several minutes, then moved straight straight upward quickly , then straight up quickly out of sight, no noise at all.... i told my mother when i got home, but then was forgotten, i've told people all of my life when the subject arose, and still tell people ....It is the truth....Many adults witnessed it that day also......It was the most increddable thing i ever wittnessed......The only thing that i have seen.....It moveed at such a speed , that i know now, that no man, or pilot could not  survive or fly such a craft.
content.summary: Bright, glowing,bright as the sun, hovered, left straight up in a instant velocity , very sudden.

content.detailedDescription: I was driving down highway 213 heading towards windfall in i was driving 65 mph..I was taking pictures of the sunset to the west i took 10 photos..A few days later i was going through them and came across one that had a ufo (its one of the best photos i've ever seen, its deffinately a must see) its very detailed and you can see the trail from where it was sitting on the side of the road and as i passed it shot up into the sky.. you can also see the object very well its grey in color and is  disc shaped..I've never seen anything like it before i've seen ufo pictures but never anything like what i've caught on camera..I snapped the shot at the most perfect time and i never seen it until i looked at my photos..I have the photo on my phone but i really don't want to put it out on the internet if your interested and would like to see it your more than welcome to contact me and come take a look i can also take you to where it happened
content.summary: Took off from road and ascended straight up

content.detailedDescription:
This lasted about 2 minutes. i was standing outside on the street talking to a neighbor, the sky was clear and though we live close to an airport, there were no other traditional air vehicles in the area. we are very familiar with the movement of air traffic in our area and this object did not move like any aircraft we've seen. the sky was clear, no clouds and was empty except for this object.

my neighbor noticed it over my shoulder so i turned around when she asked what it was. what attracted our attention was it's brightness and the rapid position changes in its flight (up, down, left, right). it appeared only bright white at first and then after a short while pulsed an additional white light, almost the same size but still a part of the sphere.  as it began moving rapidly north, a red light appeared that did not flash. then blue light appeared that did begin blinking.

at first we thought that the pulsing lights could be traditional airline lights but the very abrupt changes of direction and elevation convinced us it wasn't an airliner or a military jet.  we considered a stealth helicopter, but that seemed unlikely too. 

it started in the southeast, ascended, appeared to reverse, moved west slightly, then back toward east. it picked up speed rapidly straight north disappearing behind the trees over percy priest lake which is about a mile from where we were standing. it then shot straight east over the lake out of sight.

i've got phone video saved but was unable to transfer it to my computer.
content.flightPath: Hovering then path,Path with directional change
content.summary: Small bright sphere, first just white, then pulsating secondary light, then stable red light, then addition of flashing blue

content.detailedDescription:
My name is john and my son and i were playing catch in our backyard in somersworth, nh about 2 months ago.  my son noticed this object coming toward us from behind me.  he said, "what the heck is that" and i turned around looking for a bird or something.  i was taken aback when i noticed this object.  i am by far an expert, but i have been in the air firce for 16 years working aircraft maintenance (avionics).  i walked toward the object trying to get a better angle under it because i could not make out any wings.  the object didn't make any noise.  it was metallic color like a delorian and the glow is the sunlight reflecting off its surface.  the flight path in the picture is from right to left.  i was so fixated on trying to make out wings and what type of aircraft, that i didn't think of pictures until i noticed it approaching the tree line.  i rushed to get out my iphone and take the picture.

i am still dumbfounded on what this was.  i first thought a blimp or something because there are not any wings.  then i also see there is no pod beneath it.  i just chalked it up to a ufo.  not necessarily alien related but definitely unidentifiable.

i recently made a connection to an old video of bob lazar and how he illustrates the propulsion system and the "gravity wave" that surrounds a ship.  i then noticed the same magnetic field or gravity wave shape can be seen coming off this object in the picture.   it looks as if the reflected light is being bent around a magnetic field!

this could be nothing but i figured i could send this off to you folks to look at.  i am just a novice that doesn't "believe" but i do have an open mind and watch plenty shows and documentaries on this topic.

let me know what you all at mufon think of this picture.

v/r
john perin

sent from aol mobile mail
content.summary: Silver metallic looking craft with no noise or wings, flew over backyard of house.

content.detailedDescription: We were tubing on cedar lake when i had to stop the boat because 2 kids fell off the tube. as i cut the throttle i looked up to see 2 huge saucer like crafts one in front of the other bother were the same size. the 2nd one was trailing the 1st one by less then 1000 feet. they had no lights, no tails, no wings no noise and no vapor trails. they were less than 1000 feet above the lake just hovering. i watched them for about 1-2 min. and then i had to bring the ladder back into the boat which took maybe 20 sec,  i turned my back to the crafts, when i turned around they were gone, and no other crafts were in the area. i am retired air force of 20 years being a crew chief on kc-135's so i know what a airplane looks like.
content.summary: On cedar pond both objects were hovering above lake, one behind the other.

content.detailedDescription: Was driving on the yellow head highway between jasper national park and hinton alberta when me and my boyfriend saw a green light in the sky just as soon as we had noticed it sitting there it shot across the sky and disapeared.
content.summary: Driving and saw a light

content.detailedDescription: My wife and i were driving home from a birthday party when my wife yelled,"what's that?" i looked over my left shoulder and saw glowing red orange light. at first i thought it was a radio tower. after getting a better look i could tell it was not. i immediately pulled over to look at what i was seeing. i saw a cylinder that was glowing red orange, hovering over a lake. i grabbed my phone and took video. after about 10 seconds the glowing cylinder started to move in a diagonal path for about 5 seconds, where it began to flicker and dissappear. the video is horrible, the orange red illumination did not pick up, and i shake to much. but i got it.
content.summary: Driving and saw a hovering, glowing red orange cylinder over a lake, than slowly flew diagonal and flickers than disappeared.

content.detailedDescription: Yo estaba trabajando en casa de mi madre en compañia de un primo mio, el dia estaba demasiado soleado y hacia demasiado calor por lo cual me vi tentado a mirar al cielo cuando pude persibir esa esfera en el cielo se movia muy lenta hasta quedar quieta en un solo sitio, estaba demasiado alta, tanto que ningun avion alcanzaria esa altura a menos que sea un jet y se este moviendo, pero esa esfera se cambiaba de sitio y luego se quedaba quieta en un sitio. cuando me dio por mirar a lo ancho del cielo, pude persibir que habian aproximadamente otras 4 mas, en diferentes angulos del cielo en mi ciudad (medellin). de tiempo en tiempo se movian intercambiando de sitio, parecian con voluntad propia; para hacer estos intercambios de sitio si lo hacian a una alta velocidad, por lo menos mas rapido que un avion. yo alcance a tomar las fotos con un celular de camara con baja resolucion (moto g), pero tambien hice un video de una esfera en movimiento, esta esfera a lo ultimo se pierde en el horizonte a un alta velocidad y al verla ya mas horizontalmente se lo nota mas una forma de disco y emitiento ya una luz mas fuerte en su parte de atras, dando la impresion de turbinas o algo asi. yo habia tenido la oportunidad varios años atras en un pueblo de mi pais ver unas luces de noche con unos movimientos aterrantes pero nunca habia visto por tanto tiempo un suceso ovni como este del 11 de enero.
content.summary: Eran apriximadamente de 4 a 5 circulos y uno en disco como metalicos muy brillantes y a la vez con sombra por el sol, muy veloces y con cambio de direccion continua y se quedaban quietos por largo periodo de tiempo.

content.detailedDescription: I was walking my dog at 8:26 pm on 9-06-2015 when something caught my eye. close to 30 red orange balls of light were dancing in the sky as i looked to the east. at first i thought they were fireworks shooting up into the sky. the flickering light trail behind them said i was right. but i never heard the boom or saw the flash of fireworks. then they began changing directions like a swarm of bees. then some would disappear and as others would be there. the lights must have been a few miles away so i could not see what they were. i came back in after about 10 minutes and my cellphone and internet were having connection issues.
content.summary: A swarm of red-orange lights with dust trails moving in random patterns.

content.detailedDescription: September 5, 2015 aprox. 9 pm an unidentified craft in a dim yellow light hovered over centerville ohio i was on alex-bell and clyo rd looking west towards centerville the craft moved north to south back and forth and so on for a period of 10 minutes last thing i observed it lowered below the tree line then it shot up about a footover tree line about a 30 degree angle from my view at ground level as it reappeared the light went from a dim yellow to verry briliant white or blue with red markers at ends and in middle it then began to expel or shoot flares with red lights & white trails as i viewd this i then herd multiple sirens and police vehicles heading in that direction (west) on clyo rd oddly as soon as sirens came on the light descended and i know of no military air field in that area as wright patterson air force base is at least 30-40 minutes away in the opposite direction north east
content.summary: Craft over centerville ohio 09/05/2015 hovering and moving in figure 8 motion

content.detailedDescription: I was sitting in my bed, trying to fall asleep. i felt very uncomfortable and agitated for some reason. i felt like something was off and i couldn't get comfortable. out of the corner of my eye i saw a bright flash of light outside my window. i quickly scrambled to get my glasses and i barely got them on in time before the light disappeared. it was very large and very bright compared to the airplanes i always see and it moved way faster than anything i've ever seen in the sky. it was a whitish, blue-white, very bright glow. there was a slight, faint blue-whitish trail that was left. it was moving upwards and towards the north east before it disappeared. afterwards, my emotions were much more elevated. i felt a range of intesne emotions in a short period of time and couldn't control them. i was very agitated and internally stressed. i also felt overwhelmingly tired suddenly. i fell very abrubtly into a deep sleep within the next few minutes.
content.summary: Very large, bright orb moved very quickly across sky and disappeared

content.detailedDescription:
I was working ot on the night of the 4th of september 2014, in n franklin county.  clear night, low light pollution.  i stopped my work truck to relieve myself on a country road.  i was staring up at the stars and saw what i assumed was a satellite heading south from the n-nw, off to my right and about 30-40* overhead and just barely entering my field of view as i was facing south.  the solid white light covered 10 lateral degrees before a blue starlike light (smaller by half) descended straight down, from a fixed place, quickly and changed direction abruptly to follow no more than 10 lateral degrees behind the the white light.  there was a noticible increase in speed by about 2 lateral degrees by both objects.  after both objects covered about 30 lateral degrees a second blue starlike light, exactly like the second object, dropped quickly down from a fixed location and then changed direction to follow the first object (white bright light).  this went on for another approx. 20 degrees and the first object (bright white light) dimmed out fast and the two stralike clear blue lights split up and disappeared from my view after some distance.  this occurred in an approx. 15 second timeframe at approx. 2145-2150.  i verbally recorded my account of the event on my  iphone and still have it.

later that evening, at the end of my night, i was stationary in the work truck servicing a house and was staring at ursa major which was close to the equatorial plane.  within the four major stars that make up the "pot" and to the inside of the furthest most right top star, another blue light appeared, faint at first then more clear, dropping slowly from approx 15-20 degrees to commercial plane traffic height.  it stopped and stayed in place (from my perspective) for some time (maybe 20-30 seconds).  i had to look just to the left of it so my eyes could pick it up.  it began to flash blue, blue, blue, then red, blue, red, blue, then went white and flashed red like an airplane beacon light and slowly headed west, acting like an airplane.  it was a much longer event and it weirded me out and excited me at the same time.  i still have my recordings of what happened but haven't listened to them since and can't figure how to send them or attach them here. i ended my work night and headed back to the tri cities at about midnight i believe.

that's it.
content.summary: Solid white (satellite) chased by two blue lights descending.  blue light decending then acting as plane.

content.detailedDescription:
I was at home one winter's night watching tv with my son. my wife was on the phone talking with her sister. i heard her say 'its big and coming right towards our house'. my wife repeated herself a few times so i opened my front door, i remember my stocking feet became cold due to the residual snow on the top on my front stairs. i witnessed a large craft very slowly moving across my neighbors  property (across the road from my property). it had two large lights, like large, very bright search lights. there were two columns of light going from the craft to the ground. the lights seemed to come from two 'nosecones' for lack of a better word. these nosecones protruded from the front of the craft. i could see their outline from the stars they blocked from view. the lights moved, very slowly, in tandem like they were searching for something or someone. i could see the outline of the huge craft by the number of stars it blocked from view. the craft appeared to be moving at about 1-2 miles an hour. i couldn't believe that a craft that large was only slightly moving. it was over in less than 10 minutes from my first sighting until it was out of my view. the craft was a dark dull black in color, on the sides and bottom. i could not see the top.
i saw many aircraft, including helicopters while serving in vietnam. this craft was something i had never seen before. i marveled that i could not hear any sound coming from the craft. my tv was on at the time, so i shut it off and listened again. i heard a very low base, slight rumbling sound coming from the craft. i noticed that my ribs had began to slightly vibrate. looking at the coffee table near me i saw ripples, rings on the surface of the drink i had there. the rumble was very muffled, and i had to strain to hear it. there were no other sounds coming from the craft. there were no other lights on the craft except for the search lights.
while i had a camera i did not think to take photos of the craft and lights.
content.summary: Saw very large craft, all black but with two searchlights, moved very slowly gone in 10 min. determined outline by the stars it blocked out.

content.detailedDescription: I was driving and i saw a bright orangeish bright light in the sky and i stopped and started watching it and it moved fast to the left and then it dropped down fast then shot back up and it looked like it went behind a cloud and then it literally disappeared. i started watching it because i saw a really bright light and it was relatively close to the ground but it was right above the hudson river. it looked like it was trying to hide behind the cloud but it was gone. the lights were to bright for me to have not seen it. it was also a full moon and the sky was pretty clear so i only saw that one cloud and didn't really see another cloud after. i've always believed in ufos and this was the second time i've seen one in 3 years.
content.summary: Bright orangish hovering light moving from right to left and dropping fast then disappearing.

content.detailedDescription: When i was walking home from primary school i noticed the object just above the power lines about 20 feet above me it was a dull silver 5 pointed star shape on its flat at first i thought it was a balloon but it seemed to be on the wrong orientation for a helium ballon and much too large as it i could see the power lines in front of it.  as i stopped to look at it it stopped. i walked on watching it as i walked, it kept pace with me. i stopped again and it stopped. i lifted a stone from the ground and fired it at the object but missed. the object then went vertical upwards faster than i had ever seen anything move before and was out of sight in about 2 seconds. i was about 10 years old at the time and have never seen anything like this since, but this always disturbed me not knowing what this was. since that day i have had an interest in ufos but have never mentioned this incident to anyone except close friends until now.
content.summary: Star shaped followed me when i stopped it stopped then went vertical a high speed and out of sight

content.detailedDescription: I was awoken by the entity. i was in my bed laying on my stomach, i turned my head back at my bedroom door. when i saw it, i turned my head back facing the other way. i couldn't move after that point. my body started to feel weird, the left side of my body felt like it was being sucked into something, my vision was weird. the best way that i can describe it, a tv that has the gray, white, and black static. i can only describe it by drawing it out. what i saw looked like a grey. very skinny, a little bit taller then my bedroom door knob. it had long skinny arms but it's hands were normal sized. it's eyes were big and black, it didn't seem like it had a mouth or nose. i was calling out for help, and it felt like i couldn't really talk or scream out. at some point i was able to move around. it was just standing there in the middle of my bedroom door at starring at me.
content.summary: I was awoken by it. i felt like i couldn't move.

content.detailedDescription:
Brother pointed out a 'black dot' in the sky after we'd just finished eating, we all stared at it for a bit trying to work out if it was a drone or a balloon before my dad said we had binoculars in the house. i ran up and grabbed them, looked at the object and it turned out to be something of a manta-ray type shape. it didn't move once during the 30 minutes before it got too dark to see, not even to change the direction it was facing... no propellers, and it seemed too high up to be a drone. i tried to get a picture of it twice, once through the binoculars and again through my glasses... my phone didn't pick up the object either time, as though it wasn't even there. 
i live in a tiny village, so a lot of options were immediately crossed out. this was a strange occurrence for england.
content.summary: Black dot in sky, got binoculars, manta-ray shaped object hovering in sky

content.detailedDescription:
On tuesday september 27, 1994 at 9:05 pm i was coming home from work when i noticed what looked like a huge star moving across the horizon in the distance. 

i usually don't go that direction but i had to investigate to see what it was. after driving about a mile i reached the area i had seen it and what i saw completely caught me off guard.

over to the left of the road across from the local high school was a subdivision of houses and as i pulled up i saw a large disc about 40 to 50 feet in size hovering over top of one of them. it was shining a bluish white beam of light on the roof hovering completely silently (almost like it was suspended by ropes or something). the beam of light was coming from what looked like a rectangular shaped window on the side of it. 

i couldn't see the top of it because it was at night but the bottom of it was covered in lights and was extremely bright. in the center of the bottom was a huge red light and then the rest of the bottom was covered with small white lights. 

after a few minutes of observing it from the road i decided to get a closer look so i drove down the hill into the subdivision. at this point i was probably 50 feet away from it looking up at about a 45 degree angle. just at that moment the ufo apparently took notice i was there and slowly glided over top of another house in the opposite direction away from me. it then stopped and hovered over top of it like it did the other house.

a couple of more minutes passed (about 5 minutes total combined) and then i noticed that a car up in the school parking lot across the street started to leave. i hadn't even paid attention to it since i arrived because i was so focused on the ufo. 

i was kind of in shock because my immediate thought was "there's a ufo hovering over a house and you're just going to drive away?!". i couldn't believe anybody would do that. a few seconds after the car started driving away the ufo slowly started moving in that direction away from me almost like it was following the car.

of course i didn't want it to get away so i floored my old chevy cavalier as fast it could go out of the subdivision and back onto the main road but by the time i got up on top of the hill there was nothing. there was no trace of the ufo or car. it was like they both just vanished. 

it's been over 20 years since i witnessed that event but it's something that will be etched in my memory forever. i've done a lot of thinking about it and the only conclusion i can come to is that it wasn't from this planet. the only possible alternative would be military experimental aircraft but that doesn't explain why it was hovering over top of a house shining a bluish white beam of light on the roof with an engine that didn't make any sound.

attached is a drawing of what i witnessed using microsoft paint.
content.flightPath: Path with directional change,Path then hovering
content.summary: Witnessed a disc shaped object with very bright lights hovering over house shining beam on roof

content.detailedDescription:
I was preparing our nightly fire at our vacation trailer when i noticed an orange light in the eastern sky. as it cleared the trees i thought this is unlike anything i have ever seen in the night sky. i immediately knocked on the patio door of our trailer to get my wife's attention. she joined me in watching this object as it continued in a westerly direction. the sphere was the same color as a orange halogen streetlight. it made no sound and no deviation in flight path. it continued on it way until we lost sight of it in the trees on the horizon. at this point i turned to my wife and asked if she had ever seen anything like it before. she responded with a negative. it was an unsettling experience. 
at this point i proceeded to attempt to light our fire again when she exclaimed there is another one! coming right in the same path as the first sphere. on this one i observed yellowish light on the lower portion of the object. this sphere followed the behaviour of the first sphere in elevation and flight path. we spent the rest of the night observing the sky in case there were more spheres to be seen. no further objects were observed.
content.summary: Spheres in west central wisconsin

content.detailedDescription: I was with a group of friends in angra dos reis, a city in the state of rio de janeiro, brazil. we were doing a shamanic journey at a house by the beach. we all had experiences related to interstellar travel. my experience was that the five of us unified our consciousness and became one single geometric shape that became a pentagram and we traveled in it to other galaxies. at the end of the evening, we decided to close the ceremony with a prayer at the beach. as we finished praying, i felt an urge to turn around and face the ocean, towards east. in that moment, we all saw what looked like a splash of white light in the shape of a sphere with tail way above the horizon in the sky. it flashed and disappeared.
content.summary: We all saw what looked like a splash of white light in the shape of a sphere with tail way above the horizon in the sky. it flashed and disappeared.
content.locationName: Angra dos Reis, State of Rio de Janeiro

content.detailedDescription: I was a restaurant on silver lake boulevard with a friend. i saw two strange objects in the sky. the best way to describe it is that they looked like dna. two black strips floating in the sky, moving around each other, entwining, like a dance. as we watched and commented, other people from the restaurant saw it too. we all went out to the street to get a better look. there were people on the other side of the street watching as well. some people were parking their cars to watch it. there must have been around twenty people looking up at the sky. we were all dumbfounded, no one could come up with an explanation about what that was. we stood there for about a half hour, watching it. then decided to had back to work and lost sight of it.
content.summary: I saw two strange objects in the sky. the best way to describe it is that they looked like dna. two black strips floating in the sky, moving around each other, entwining, like a dance.

content.detailedDescription:
I was walking after a late dinner with  a friend and sat down on a bench overlooking the ocean, i was pointing out plants and stars when i saw the outline and part of the body of a very large dark cigar shaped craft that literally disappeared in an instant.  immediately multiple glowing orbs stated darting around in multiple direction flashing beams of light and emitting a pulsating glow........Unlike anything i've ever seen; that went on for at least 20 minutes.  i could tell the cigar shaped  craft was still there; it was as if it was cloaked or something and there would be these very slight electrical charges that were orangish and i would see a partial outline of the ship; that happened at least 3-4 times over the course of the event.  after about 20 minute i started to feel an incredibly intense fear......Almost primal not coming from within me but from the event.....I wasnt scared from what i was seeing, but it was almost like an energy was creeping into me ... it was so intense that we immediately left.  we left before the event was over and after about ten minutes i felt an overwhelming calm as if i had been in an intense battle and was now safe.  
i swear this statement is true and accurate
content.flightPath: Hovering then path,Path with directional change,Path then hovering
content.summary: I saw a very large cigar shaped craft appear and cruise slowly ....Then disappear as if cloaked the multiple orbs appeared and went crazy zipping about and shooting beams, every so often i would an electricity flash and see the outline of the cigar craft

content.detailedDescription: I was at a house in silver lake, by the pool with a friend. the object flew above us in a straight line. it seemed close, a little over the tree tops. even thought it went by fast, i was able to see details. it's shape was circular with a long and thin rectangle attached to one side. it seemed thin like an upright saucer shape. the circular portion was light green. it's surface reminded me of a sea shell. it was beautiful and pearlescent. it had a design: a small circle in the center with curvy lines coming out of the center to the periphery. the rectangle was adjoined to one side the circle and it was bright pink. unfortunately, i was the only one who saw it. my friend didn't have her glasses on but she said she saw something passing by, as it seemed really close.
content.summary: It's shape was circular with a long and thin rectangle attached to one side. it seemed thin like an upright saucer.

content.detailedDescription: I was by the pool at a friend's house in silver lake. saw a strange shaped object in the sky. it's shape was like an inverted u, bright pink, lit from within, with fuzzy edges. it was falling down like a leaf, very slowly, floating around. i watched it together with 2 other people, for at least a half hour. the first thing i thought was that it was a bunch of gas balloons that got loose. but as i watched, and as it switched directions, floating around, i could see it from different angles and it became quite clear it was not balloons. the edges were fuzzy, like a a stuffed animal. it was lit from within and very bright pink. i was in awe and wondering what kind of object that was. it felt like a dream.
content.summary: it's shape was like an inverted u, bright pink, lit from within, with fuzzy edges. it was falling down like a leaf, very slowly, floating around. i watched it together with 2 other people, for at least a half hour.

content.detailedDescription: Upon returning from shopping and eating (no alcohol consumed) i noticed a very bright star in the sky, after further observance i realized it was moving but in a path of no commercial air vehicle.  i called my husband over who has served in the military and is very familiar with air crafts and he at first dismissed it, i began recording on my samsung s6 showed him the video and he was speechless, for over 4 minutes i recorded the object in what seemed like an erratic dancing pattern across the night sky, getting brighter then dimmer and disappearing.  this isn't the first time i've witnessed an object in this area (not exact location but near by).  please have a look at the video and let me know your thoughts, there are some bugs flying across the lense and you will hear the pool pump humming and cut off in the background, the rest are crickets and other night creatures, i wish i had better equipment (watching the video on my phone you can clearly see the stars vs the object).  i know i'm not crazy!  best wishes.  g
content.flightPath: Stationary,Hovering then path,Path with directional change,Path then hovering
content.summary: Looked like a star but 3-5x larger blinking, but changing color and moving in circular patterns

content.detailedDescription:
Driving down centerville turnpike in chesapeake in the middle of nowhere at 8:30 pm on a saturday evening when 4 orange glowing craft appear flying toward us in the sky racing around each other then make a sharp right turn and go up into the sky and disappear.

the objects were large and obvious ~ impossible to miss as they were right in front of us.  i had just been telling my husband earlier that day about sightings in virginia beach. so, at first he said well, there you go!  then, the objects stayed and you couldn't deny they were not aircraft or flares. they were racing around each other in all sorts of 'quick' directional changes. we watched, perplexed until they took a sharp right turn and flew upward and disappeared.

they were behind us now and i was viewing them though the sunroof of the van.
content.summary: Driving down deserted highway middle of nowhere, 4 orange glowing craft appear flying toward us in the sky racing around each other then make a sharp right turn and disappear

content.detailedDescription: At approximately 12:30am my husband and i went out on our back deck to look at the stars. in the southeast, i noticed a star that was flickering and appeared to move slightly.  i called my husband over to look at it and he remarked that it was flickering a lot. he sat down and i began looking at the other stars in the sky and they were not flickering  like the other "star" i observed. at approximately 1:00am, my husband decided to go inside and ready himself for bed. i was curious about the odd star and sat in a chair and observed it for nearly 45 minutes. after watching it for 10 minutes, above a large white pine tree used as a point of reference, it became apparent it was not a star, but an object hovering and ver, very, slowly moving. the object moved first to the west but stayed in relatively the same area, but it would slowly migrated east, then down. two airplanes flew nearby this hovering object and the object's lights became brighter. over the course of nearly 45 minutes the objec ultimately ended up in the east.  it was still hovering, but i became too tired to observe it further.  it seemed like it was almost trying to look like a star by only moving very slowly.
content.summary: Hovering ufo that slowly changed direction

content.detailedDescription:
I was cutting a movie gofast 2014 hd onboard cameras for my youtube video  and recognized, that something strange appeard in front of the rocket and suddenly i saw, that a disk passed the rocket. 

the gofast 2014 rocket officially set a new world record on july 14, 2014 at 7:32am as the highest and fastest amateur rocket ever launched into space.

analysis of the data from the recovered military grade inertial measurement unit (imu) that flew onboard shows that the gofast rocket reached 385,800 feet above mean sea level (73.1 miles) and hit a top speed of 3,580 miles per hour. the old record held by the csxt’s gofast 2004 rocket was 72 miles with a top speed of 3,420 mph.

the gofast 2014 imu had flown successfully on four commercial space missions at white sands missile range (wsmr) in new mexico and was calibrated using c-band transponder us army radar tracking data prior to its flight into space on the gofast rocket july 14, 2014. statistical analysis of the wsmr flights and the gofast 2014 launch verifies the 73.1 miles attained by the gofast rocket has a variation of 0.6 miles with a confidence level of 95%.
content.summary: The event took place during the flight of a privat rocket at black rock desert

content.detailedDescription: my son and i were traveling southbound on the new york state thruway near albany, we both saw an enormous v-shaped/boomerang shaped white object i questioned whether it was an airplane but knew right away it was no airplanes. we only saw it for several seconds before it absolutely unequivocally disappeared in mid air. it did not fly away...It disappeared like a magic act. it was there and then it was gone. there were other people on the highway so i can only assume that we were not the only ones who saw this...
content.summary: V shaped boomerang , appeared white
